什么经济衰退？ https://ritholtz.com/2023/06/what-recession/Barry Ritholtz Mon, 26 Jun 2023 13:30:57 +0000 Data AnalysisMacro/Econ https://ritholtz.com/?p=315425 <p>利率上升、储蓄下降、赤字增加、GDP 可疑：自从收益率曲线倒挂和“经济即将衰退”的警告弥漫之后，费城联储的州重合指数地图就提供了美国经济状况的实时快照。经济。周五的发布可能已经过去了，但它充满了积极的惊喜……</p><p> <a class="button" href="https://ritholtz.com/2023/06/what-recession/">Read More<i class="icon ion-arrow-right-c"></i></a></p><p>帖子<a rel="nofollow" href="https://ritholtz.com/2023/06/what-recession/">什么是衰退？</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://ritholtz.com">大图片</a>上。</p> ; <p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/State-Coinc-May-2023-2.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-315429" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/State-Coinc-May-2023-2.png" alt="" width="720" height="581" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/State-Coinc-May-2023-2.png 1486w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/State-Coinc-May-2023-2-300x242.png 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/State-Coinc-May-2023-2-1024x827.png 1024w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/State-Coinc-May-2023-2-768x620.png 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/State-Coinc-May-2023-2-250x202.png 250w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></a></p><p></p><p><em>利率上升、储蓄下降、赤字增加、GDP 可疑</em>：自从收益率曲线倒挂和“经济即将衰退”的警告弥漫之后，费城联储的<a href="https://ritholtz.com/?s=State+Coincident+Indexes" target="_blank" rel="noopener">州重合指数</a>地图就提供了美国经济状况的实时快照。经济。周五的发布可能已经过去了，但它充满了值得关注的积极惊喜。</p><p>概述很简单：在过去 3 个月中，所有 50 个州指数的一致指数均有所增加（扩散指数 = 100）。上个月（2023 年 5 月），50 个州中有 47 个州的指数上涨，2 个州（明尼苏达州和罗德岛州）持平，只有 1 个州（威斯康星州）下跌。其他表现疲软的州包括新泽西州、阿肯色州和肯塔基州。</p><p>内德·戴维斯研究公司 (Ned Davis Research) 将州重合指数整理成概率图表，显示我们目前陷入衰退的可能性只有 1%。这不是预测，而是将一致指数解读为当前衰退指标。</p><p> <strong>NDR 衰退概率模型：目前衰退的可能性为 1%</strong><br /> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ndr-rec-1.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-315470" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ndr-rec-1.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="488" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ndr-rec-1.jpg 982w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ndr-rec-1-300x203.jpg 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ndr-rec-1-768x520.jpg 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ndr-rec-1-250x169.jpg 250w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></a><br /> NDR 通过<a href="https://twitter.com/RyanDetrick/status/1673094052609241094" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ryan Detrick</a></p><p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><br />旁注</span>：收益率曲线似乎已经永远倒挂了。请注意， <a href="https://fred.stlouisfed.org/graph/?g=16sgK" target="_blank" rel="noopener">10 年期减去 3 个月期</a>国债——<a href="https://www.fuqua.duke.edu/faculty/campbell-harvey" target="_blank" rel="noopener">杜克大学福卡商学院</a>教授 <a href="https://ritholtz.com/2021/09/mib-campbell-harvey-on-defi/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">哈维·坎贝尔 (Harvey Campbell)</a>创建的衰退预测指标在 2019 年出现倒挂，然后在 2020 年再次出现短暂倒挂，然后在 FOMC 于 2022 年开始加息后进一步加深：</p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/10-Year-T-Minus-3-Month-ann.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-315478" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/10-Year-T-Minus-3-Month-ann.png" alt="" width="720" height="246" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/10-Year-T-Minus-3-Month-ann.png 1318w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/10-Year-T-Minus-3-Month-ann-300x102.png 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/10-Year-T-Minus-3-Month-ann-1024x350.png 1024w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/10-Year-T-Minus-3-Month-ann-768x262.png 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/10-Year-T-Minus-3-Month-ann-250x85.png 250w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></a></p><p></p><p>尽管历史上对衰退的预测近乎完美，但在联邦基金十年为零的情况下，收益率曲线反转的预言性也许就不那么明显了。无论如何，客观地看待当前数据并表明我们目前或很快就会陷入衰退是极其困难的。</p><p>通配符？联邦公开市场委员会在多大程度上过度收紧利率并通过未来加息太快/太多/太高而导致经济衰退……</p><p></p><p></p><p> <em>Previously</em> :<br /><a href="https://ritholtz.com/2022/06/recession-no/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">我们正处于衰退之中吗？ （否）</a> （2022 年 6 月 1 日）</p><p><a href="https://ritholtz.com/2022/09/data-nber-recession/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">哪些数据让 NBER 预测经济衰退？</a> （2022 年 9 月 1 日）</p><p><a href="https://ritholtz.com/2022/01/the-post-normal-economy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">后正常经济</a>（2022 年 1 月 7 日）</p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/2023/05/10-bad-takes-on-this-market/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这个市场的 10 个糟糕的情况</a>（2023 年 5 月 19 日）</p><p></p><p><em>资料来源</em>：<br /> <a href="https://www.philadelphiafed.org/surveys-and-data/regional-economic-analysis/state-coincident-indexes" target="_blank" rel="noopener">状态重合指数当前报告</a>( <a href="https://www.philadelphiafed.org/-/media/frbp/assets/surveys-and-data/coincident/2023/coincidentindexes0523.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PDF</a> )<br />费城联邦储备银行，2023 年 5 月</p><p></p><p>帖子<a rel="nofollow" href="https://ritholtz.com/2023/06/what-recession/">什么是衰退？</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://ritholtz.com">大图片</a>上。</p> ;
